data.description: ONE LEVEL LIVING at its finest, in the sought after community the FARMS AT HUNTING CREEK!  The community has over 100 homes all on upwards of 1 acre lots or more, sidewalks, a playground, basketball court, sports field, & a beautiful lake.  This ranch style home with fully finished lower level has it all!  The beautifully appointed kitchen opens to a cozy family room with gas fireplace. Kitchen cabinets have built in organizers, granite counters & large island. Enjoy double ovens for entertaining, built in microwave & 4 burner gas cook top. The primary bedroom & attached en suite bath offers dual vanities. large tub, & HUGE walk in fully tiled shower.  Main level also offers 2 other great size bedrooms, upgraded full bath, & laundry room.  Escape to the lower level with bedroom 4 & full bath, massive recreation room to use however you'd like, and separate Theater Room space. This home offers almost 2 ACRES, which is a larger lot than most in the neighborhood. The home sits at the end of the street with added seclusion! 3 CAR GARAGE with ELECTRIC CAR CHARGER & long driveway with extra room for parking. All this & SOLAR PANELS included on Power Purchase Agreement lowering your total electric bills, currently less than $200/per month.  Zoned for award winning Huntingtown High School & Plum Point Middle School, offering quick access to Prince Frederick for shopping, & an easy commute to DC, Annapolis, PAX River NAS, Andrews AFB, etc.  This home is a must see!
